OL,3,CProgramme listings for MON 4 MAY
OL,4,G1405FWish Me Luck
OL,5,     GVivien, Emily, and Colin
OL,6,     Gparachute into France; Colin
OL,7,     Ginjures his ankle. Vivien poses
OL,8,     Gas nanny, Emily stays with Marie,
OL,9,     Graising suspicion. Colin kills a
OL,10,     GMilice woman. In England, Liz
OL,11,     Grejects Kit.
OL,12,G1510FRewind Time Machine
OL,13,     GIn 1970 schoolchildren are
OL,14,     Ginterviewed over smoking and
OL,15,     Gwhether they like the habit or
OL,16,     Gnot.
OL,17,G1513FHank the Cowboy
OL,18,     GFrancis Coudrill presents a
OL,19,     Gunique blend of animation and the
OL,20,     GEuropean Western in this TV
OL,21,     Gclassic as Hank Rides Again.
