OL,8,G1800FSpace 1999
OL,9,     GHumans from another planet,
OL,10,     Gfrozen for 300 years, are
OL,11,     Grecovered and revived.
OL,12,G1905FDanger Man
OL,13,     GA foreign senator is murdered in
OL,14,     Gthe presence of his blind
OL,15,     Grelative, Josetta. Rioting ensues
OL,16,     Gdue to a rumor that the American
OL,17,     Ggovernment was behind the
OL,18,     Gkilling, and secret agent John
OL,19,     GDrake is sent in.
