OL,4,G2035FSecond Thoughts
OL,5,     GBill is fed up with Joe being
OL,6,     Ginconsiderate, and Faith
OL,7,     Gcontrives to reunite Richard and
OL,8,     GMarjorie.
OL,9,G2105FDrop The Dead Donkey
OL,10,     GIt's party time for GlobeLink:
OL,11,     Gthe razz at the British News
OL,12,     GAwards ceremony begins. Damian
OL,13,     Gdreams of victory, Dave dreams of
OL,14,     GHelen, and for once Henry is less
OL,15,     Gthan happy to be centre-stage.
OL,16,G2135FDrop The Dead Donkey
OL,17,     GAfter a sudden death at
OL,18,     GGlobeLink, Gus goes into exercise
OL,19,     Goverdrive to try to defer his own
OL,20,     Gdemise. Meanwhile, George tries
OL,21,     Ghis hand at acting; and Damien
OL,22,     Ghas trouble with his Porsche.
